highlights.text: Breizaas has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Dama Fra Bygda” is the highest at #15.
“Everything is romantic featuring caroline polachek” by Charli xcx and Caroline Polachek is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #95.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 100 days straight.
“Doot Doot (6 7) (Bonus Track)” by Skrilla is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 17 spots at #82.
